## Important

Please ensure you follow the schedule, and don't delay out of courtesy for another team. Even five minutes could throw things out of whack. 
If you need an admin, get help via the `#sixes-support` in our Discord.

You will need to book your own game server, preferably from ozfortress. You can learn how to do so using the button above labelled "Booking a *x* server". To learn how to execute the configs, see the button above "How to use the Round Timer configs".

